arChildNodes.szComment:
Neyrelle looks back at them with tears in her eyes. She lowers the stone as LION AKARAT watches on. 
Bright light fills the body as the magic works. At last, Neyrelle is untethered from the soulstone.
 It is cathartic and big. Her tears spill.
Eru is kneeled down on the ground, his hands held up above himself in meditative prayer.
